'''巨爪地懶'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Megalonyx}}''）是[[中新世|中新世]]晚期至[[更新世|更新世]]晚期一[[屬|屬]]已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[地懶|地懶]]。牠們的近親為[[二趾樹懶|二趾樹懶]]。牠們是[[北美洲|北美洲]]的[[特有種|特有種]]，是[[二趾樹懶科|二趾樹懶科]]下分佈最廣的，最北至[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Stock, C.|year=1942|title=A ground sloth in Alaska|journal=Science|volume=95|pages=552-3}}</ref>及[[育空|育空]]。<ref>{{cite journal en|last=McDonald|first=H. G.|coauthors=Harington, C. R.; De Iuliis, G.|title=The Ground Sloth Megalonyx from Pleistocene Deposits of the Old Crow Basin, Yukon, Canada|journal=Arctic|volume=53|issue=3|pages=213–20|publisher=The Arctic Institute of North America|location=Calgary, Alberta|url=http://pubs.aina.ucalgary.ca/arctic/Arctic53-3-213.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-08-16|date=September 2000|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703013709/http://pubs.aina.ucalgary.ca/arctic/Arctic53-3-213.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>牠們是由{{link-en|游地懶|Pliometanastes}}[[演化|演化]]而來，其下最早出現的物種是''M. wheatleyi''。模式種傑氏巨爪地懶（''M. jeffersonii''）體長可達 {{convert|3|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重則超過 1,000 [[公斤|公斤]]<ref name="library.sandiegozoo.org">{{Cite web |url=http://library.sandiegozoo.org/factsheets/_extinct/sloth_extinct/extinct_sloth.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214074751/http://library.sandiegozoo.org/factsheets/_extinct/sloth_extinct/extinct_sloth.htm |archive-date=2015-02-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
 
==化石==
